{"tid":1989811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荔枝角手足有事要請大家注意","createTime":"2020-04-26T09:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T07:43:40.000Z","uid":353501,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e471f87cd07286b9e411cafd409fc6323f2869a0","tid":1989811,"uid":353501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"全文如下：<br />\n各位香港人：<br />\n    前排有人冒稱被拘押手足家人，網上眾籌律師費。<br />\n    經過我哋多番調查後發現募捐者曾經倒賣文具，收錢不發貨，我哋查出該募捐者身份：<br />\n    何泳龍，身份證：Z95xxx (x) ,出生 1988年9月x日。佢宜家正正喺荔枝角拘押所，編號1188-2x<br />\n   唔單止係咁，紅導演仲探佢，唔知淡D咩野，有見及此，所有牆外手足小心紅粉。<br />\n   同埋牆內手足，唔缺律師，而且我哋家人如有經濟上困難都會同立法會議員講，請大家唔好被騙。<br />\n   最後，我哋牆內手足，忽忘初心，絕對唔會被高牆埋沒意志。<br />\n   香港人反抗<br />\n   香港人團結<br />\n                                                                  阿拔<br />\n                                                                 Apr 18 2020<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0DS4iz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0DS4iz.png&h=8ee27e8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b277b46d5c86a15e591d6bfbad62c7b167d2d305","tid":1989811,"uid":353501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:04:51.000Z","msg":"另外阿拔有少少說話想寄語香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103419337687469/posts/251080946254640/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103419337687469%2Fposts%2F251080946254640%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=6c58a8e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103419337687469/posts/251080946254640/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"bb59e8079c690b00715ef784a5aaf2b3b6847898","tid":1989811,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a678e5ee357fd4f7ffa9bac9d754c20c9e681b","tid":1989811,"uid":262406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T09:06:58